    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am so excited to show you this absolute gem! I have babied this car since the moment I got it, and it\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape that it still feels brand new. Not a single scratch on the paint and the interior is totally spotless\u2014it even still has that fresh car smell! It drives like a dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage its whole life. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect, you've found it! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself! \u2728",
