    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS to produce a linear 333 hp. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock for precise torque distribution. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension featuring OEM bushings to preserve factory-spec kinematics. Finished in original paint with zero bolster wear on the Nappa leather, this M3 offers an uncompromised analog driving experience with an 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically synchronized and aesthetically flawless.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
