    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously garaged its entire life, preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks or stone chips, recently protected by a premium ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule: the leather remains supple with no bolster wear, the dashboard is pristine, and all electronics function with factory precision. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio with every maintenance interval performed at the dealership. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this is a rare, investment-grade example for the most discerning enthusiast. No accidents, no modifications, just perfection.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
