    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Meticulously maintained and free of any aesthetic or mechanical imperfections, it offers an unparalleled driving experience. This is a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade example that satisfies the most exacting standards of excellence.",
