    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this absolute beauty in person. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and has been kept in absolutely pristine, showroom-level shape\u2014not a scratch or a worry to be found! It drives like a total dream and honestly feels brand new. I'm looking for a good home for it, so if you want a ride that\u2019s been truly pampered, this is the one. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
