    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving German engineering, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L straight-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential for optimal torque bias. The chassis integrity is absolute, benefiting from comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a suspension system featuring high-rate springs and precision-valved dampers. Every mechanical interface\u2014from the hydraulic steering rack to the cross-drilled braking system\u2014operates with factory-new tolerances. With zero fluid seepage and a flawlessly maintained valvetrain, this vehicle offers a pure, visceral driving experience in a showroom-quality state.",
